name: Umpass-stay
Lore: 'Klatooinian born into slavery to Desilijic Hutt clan on Shawti. Musician. Works as a spy for Jabba at his desert fortress while playing drums for visiting bands.',
Text: 'Power +2 at a Jabba''s Palace site. Each of your other musicians at same site is power +2 and immune to attrition < 3. Immune to attrition < 4.',
